## SoundFont Samples

Peach includes a custom SoundFont file (`Samples.sf2`) assembled from two
open-source sources:

### FluidR3_GM (Piano Presets)

The following presets are sourced from FluidR3_GM:

- Yamaha Grand Piano (bank 0, program 0)
- Bright Yamaha Grand (bank 0, program 1)
- Electric Piano (bank 0, program 2)

